{"tid":849155,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"最早BT種子 15年後仍能下載","createTime":"2018-10-05T12:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T10:09:23.000Z","uid":49648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb9ab792571cb812543f4702bb083467ddf3ce7","tid":849155,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/205035_940fdc27901ba7b38480e785a323fe05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F205035_940fdc27901ba7b38480e785a323fe05.png&h=7506a746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】現時不少人利用BT種子，下載及分享影音或其他大容量檔案，檔案愈多人下載，下載速度就愈快。有科技發燒友近日發現，由新西蘭一名IT人十五年前建立、被視為最早出現的BT種子，在現今高速寬頻及串流技術盛行的情況下，竟仍可以運作，令科技迷驚奇。<br />\n該個BT種子源於二○○三年，當時一群新西蘭影迷拍攝了向科幻電影《22世紀殺人網絡》致敬的短片，雖然他們把容量壓縮至150MB，但在高速寬頻尚未普及的年代，傳送這檔案仍需支付高昂上網費。<br />\n其中一名熟悉IT的影迷於是開發一種新技術，將短片檔案分割成無數個小檔案存放在多台電腦，並將小檔案的「種子」上傳互聯網供人下載，全球首個BT種子就此誕生。該種子至今仍有人下載和不斷「造種」，繼續運作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有沒有人有seed，想下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3186da38a33e0c8c62a98ad418a291d86e114c5c","tid":849155,"uid":214911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"1254b222b6491ce48442a69dc70ea5d45feb7140","tid":849155,"uid":73,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/224513_edec51e39e7225bf40eed374824389d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F224513_edec51e39e7225bf40eed37482438